      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "0.3 - PFKEY DEFINITION PANELS"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "This panel displays the current settings of the PF keys and allows"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "you to change them.  You change a PF key definition by typing over"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the current definition."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PF keys may be defined as any SPF/PC primary or line command. This"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "enables the user to assign frequently used repetative commands like"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\":i\", line insert, to a PF key for later recall with a single"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "keystroke."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "1 +- Display greater detail on PFKey Definition Panel"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "2 +- Describe definition of the entire keyboard"
      },
